##
## Next Generation OLTP DBMS Research
## -------------------------------------------------------

More information and documenation is available at:

http://hstore.cs.brown.edu

## -------------------------------------------------------
## RUNNING A BENCHMARK
## -------------------------------------------------------

Available benchmarks: tpcc, markov, tm1, auctionmark

(1) First build the entire distribution:

    $ ant build

(2) Next make the project jar file. You will need to do this step everytime you 
    change the benchmark source code in $HSTORE_DIR/tests/

    $ export HSTORE_BENCHMARK=tm1
    $ ant hstore-prepare -Dproject=$HSTORE_BENCHMARK

(3) You can now execute the benchmark locally on your machine with two partitions

    $ ant hstore-benchmark -Dproject=$HSTORE_BENCHMARK

## -------------------------------------------------------
## VIEWING CATALOG
## -------------------------------------------------------

$ ant catalog-viewer -Dproject=$HSTORE_BENCHMARK

